#ROOM
Vnum     30051
Name     &wThe Moonshrine Ruins - entry&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     You enter a massive, open-air temple that has collapsed into the 
sea. Moonlight filters through the cracks in the ceiling, reflecting 
off the dark water. Murloc priests have built a crude altar over 
the ruins of a Moonwell.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    30050
Desc      Sarevess's Sanctum.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    30052
Desc      The ritual grounds.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 30001 10 30051
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     30052
Name     &wThe Ritual Grounds&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The sound of monotonous chanting echoes from the shadows. Large 
jars of shadow-energy sit on the stone floor, pulsing with a dim 
purple light.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    30051
Desc      The entry ruins.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    30054
Desc      Gelihast's Altar.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    30053
Desc      A small storage room.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 30012 10 30052
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     30053
Name     &wTemple Storage Room&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Crates of ritual components are stacked here. Sacks of sand, 
jars of squid ink, and bundles of kelp are neatly organized.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    30052
Desc      Return to the ritual grounds.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 30009 10 30053
Reset O 0 30033 1 30053
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     30054
Name     &wGelihast's Altar&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Gelihast stands atop a jagged piece of obsidian, his four arms 
waving in a frantic, hypnotic dance. He is surrounded by his 
murloc followers, all chanting in their wet, gurgling language.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    30052
Desc      The ritual grounds.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    30055
Desc      The Twilight's Hammer tunnels.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 30012 1 30054
  Reset G 1 30024 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     30055
Name     &xTwilight Tunnels - Entrance&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The architecture here turns dark and jagged. Purple silk banners 
hang from the ceiling, and the air is thick with the scent of 
ozone and shadow magic.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    30054
Desc      Gelihast's Altar.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    30056
Desc      The cultist corridor.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 30002 10 30055
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     30056
Name     &xCultist Corridor - North&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Twilight cultists in dark robes pace this hallway, clutching 
iron-bound staves. To the east and west are rooms where the 
Hammer conducts its most secretive business.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    30055
Desc      The tunnel entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    30057
Desc      A dark laboratory.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    30058
Desc      Baron Aquanis's Gate.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 30002 10 30056
Reset O 0 30030 5 30056
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     30057
Name     &xThe Void Laboratory&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A large, glass vat sits in the center of the room, filled with 
swirling shadow energy. This is where the Hammer experiments 
with corrupting the natural spirits of the deep.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    30056
Desc      Return to the corridor.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 30018 10 30057
Reset O 0 30021 1 30057
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     30058
Name     &bThe Inner Gate - Baron Aquanis&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive, shimmering wall of water blocks the path forward. 
Baron Aquanis, a towering water elemental, stands guard over 
the gate, his form constantly shifting and roiling.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    30056
Desc      The cultist corridor.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    30059
Desc      The deep reservoirs.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 30013 1 30058
  Reset G 1 30031 5
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     30059
Name     &bThe Deep Reservoirs - Entrance&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The air is so humid that water drips from your armor. These 
reservoirs are ancient elven storage tanks, now reclaimed by 
the sea.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    30058
Desc      Baron Aquanis's Gate.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    30060
Desc      The reservoir continues.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 30005 10 30059
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     30060
Name     &bDeep Reservoir - Center&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The path is a narrow stone walkway suspended over a dark, 
bottomless pit of water. Massive, shark-like shapes move 
just beneath the surface.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    30059
Desc      The entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    30062
Desc      Old Serra'kis's Den.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    30061
Desc      A small maintenance alcove.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 30003 10 30060
Reset O 0 30028 10 30060
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     30061
Name     &bMaintenance Alcove&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A quiet, dark room filled with old elven tools and rusted 
iron chains.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    30060
Desc      Return to the reservoir.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 30004 10 30061
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     30062
Name     &bOld Serra'kis's Den&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This massive, underwater cavern is the lair of Old Serra'kis. 
The multi-headed hydra lunges from the depths, its jaws 
snapping with terrifying speed.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    30060
Desc      The reservoir center.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    30063
Desc      The Sanctum of the Prophecy entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 30014 1 30062
  Reset G 1 30020 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     30063
Name     &MThe Sanctum of the Prophecy - Entry&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The walls are covered in ancient, glowing scripts that detail 
the coming of the Old Gods. Twilight Lord Kelris's presence 
is felt as a heavy, oppressive weight in the air.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    30062
Desc      Serra'kis's Den.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    30064
Desc      The sanctum corridor.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 30007 10 30063
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     30064
Name     &MThe Sanctum Corridor&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Elite cultists in black plate armor stand guard here. The 
sound of a deep, rhythmic humming vibrates through the stone.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    30063
Desc      The entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    30066
Desc      Kelris's Chamber.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    30065
Desc      The Library of Shadows.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 30017 10 30064
Reset O 0 30026 1 30064
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     30065
Name     &MThe Library of Shadows&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Hundreds of dusty, leather-bound books are arranged on stone 
shelves. They contain the dark secrets and prophecies of the 
Twilight's Hammer.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    30064
Desc      Return to the corridor.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 30018 10 30065
Reset O 0 30025 5 30065
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     30066
Name     &MTwilight Lord Kelris's Chamber&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Kelris levitates in the center of the room, his form shifting 
between reality and shadow. He is surrounded by four massive 
braziers that burn with a cold, violet flame.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    30064
Desc      The sanctum corridor.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    30067
Desc      The descent to the Maw.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 30015 1 30066
  Reset G 1 30021 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     30067
Name     &MThe Descent to the Maw - entry&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The stairs here are built of black obsidian and lead toward 
the very bottom of the Deeps. The roar of a titanic beast 
echoes from below.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    30066
Desc      Kelris's Chamber.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    30068
Desc      The final ritual hall.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 30017 10 30067
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     30068
Name     &MThe Final Ritual Hall&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This hall is filled with the most fanatical of the Twilight's 
Hammer cultists. They prepare for the final summoning of 
their master's greatest servant.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    30067
Desc      Return to the ascent.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    30069
Desc      The hall continues north.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 30018 10 30068
Reset O 0 30030 10 30068
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     30069
Name     &MThe Final Ritual Hall - North&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The walls here are covered in demonic scripts that drip with 
a glowing, green liquid. The wailing sound of the Deeps is 
at its most intense here.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    30068
Desc      The southern hall.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    30070
Desc      The threshold of the Maw.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 30017 10 30069
Reset O 0 30029 10 30069
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     30070
Name     &MThe Threshold of the Maw&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive iron gate blocks the path forward. It requires the 
Blackfathom Key to unlock, or a great deal of force to bypass. 
The air smells of salt and ozone.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    30069
Desc      The ritual hall.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    30071
Desc      Aku'mai's Maw.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 30017 10 30070
Reset O 0 30034 1 30070
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     30071
Name     &MAku'mai's Maw - Final Lair&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     You stand at the bottom of the Deeps. Aku'mai, the massive, 
three-headed hydra servant of the Old Gods, rises from the 
dark water, his heads snapping with primal fury.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    30070
Desc      Return to the threshold.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 30016 1 30071
#ENDROOM

